Reviews.Title: great product
Reviews.Author: tried it
Reviews.Content: If you are thanking about hooking up your own Cctv system don't hesitate to buy this RG59 cable, It work great. It has a black outer coating with red and black power feed wire.

Reviews.Title: cable
Reviews.Author: mkcmmyers
Reviews.Content: Recieved this product earlier than expected. Product works as expected and is accurate to a degree. I would purchase this product in the future if needed.

Reviews.Title: Best deal for the price!
Reviews.Author: J F
Reviews.Content: Great quality, bare copper conductors and not CCS or CCA. Easy pull from box and has footage markings printed in white on the black jacket.

20AWG Coxial Center Conductor with 95% Coverage Braid Shield
